  "worklog": "## 2026-03-30 06:08 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 2] V4 DEPLOYED LIVE \u2014 3 Changes Applied\n\n**Task:** Deploy V4 package to live PM bot. All 3 changes had been designed, patched, and tested in prior heartbeats. Deploy early (5h before active trading) to catch any crashes.\n\n**Changes deployed:**\n1. **Copy boost disabled** (`copy_conviction_boost = 0`) \u2014 bot farms were poisoning signal, WR 77% without vs 45% with\n2. **VWAP relaxation at 11h/12h** \u2014 hour-adaptive: relaxed at peak WR hours (88%/82%), mandatory at 19h/20h. Recovers est. $18/day in blocked signals.\n3. **Fear & Greed integration** \u2014 edge modifier (+0.10 at F&G=8) and position multiplier (1.25x at F&G=8). Refreshes hourly.\n\n**Deployment log:**\n```\n06:11:01 - \ud83d\udcca F&G: 8 (Extreme Fear) \u2192 edge mod +0.10, size 1.25x\n06:11:01 - \ud83d\udcb0 CLOB Balance: $922.45\n06:11:02 - \ud83d\udcca Bootstrapped 100 candles\n06:11:02 - \ud83d\udd01 Entering main trading loop...\n```\n\n**V4 impact estimate (combined):**\n- VWAP relaxation: +$18/day from unblocked 11h/12h trades\n- Copy disabled: WR improvement from ~55% \u2192 ~65%+ (removing 45% WR noise trades)\n- F&G at current 8: +0.10 edge \u2192 more marginal trades pass threshold + 1.25x size\n- Conservative combined estimate: $25-40/day (up from $20-30/day W13)\n\n**Rollback plan:** `cp trading_bot.py.v3.3.bak trading_bot.py` and restart screen.\n\n**Monitoring plan:**\n- 06-11h UTC: verify bot runs stable, no crashes, log output clean\n- 11h UTC: first active hour \u2014 watch for VWAP_RELAXED log lines and F&G edge adjustments\n- End of day: compare V4 day WR vs V3.3 average\n\n**Next P2 heartbeat:** Monitor V4 during 11h active hour. Check first trades for VWAP_RELAXED, F&G edge mod, and outcomes.\n\n## 2026-03-30 05:38 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] Copy Signal Following Bot Farms \u2014 Confirmed Root Cause\n\n**Task:** Investigate WHY copy signal hurts WR. Analyze the top wallet database feeding the signal.\n\n**Finding:** **ALL 20 \"top\" wallets in the copy intelligence database are bot farm wallets with $0 earnings.**\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|-------|\n| Wallets with exactly 30 trades | 11 |\n| Wallets with exactly 60 trades | 7 |\n| Wallets with exactly 90 trades | 2 |\n| Wallets with positive earnings | **0** |\n| Biggest loser | \"Warped-Cloak\": -$50,285 |\n\nPerfect multiples of 30 = coordinated bot farm (identified in Mar 29 bug fix but wallet list never refreshed). The copy intelligence pipeline is: bot farm wallets \u2192 copy-signals.json \u2192 live-signals.json \u2192 conviction boost in trading_bot.py \u2192 WORSE WR.\n\nCurrent live signal: 88% bearish confidence based on 47/50 down signals from these bot wallets. This is noise, not alpha.\n\n**Signal chain audit:**\n- `pm-copy-scanner.py` (30 min cron) \u2192 produces bot-farm-polluted wallet list\n- `copy_scanner_v2.py` (5 min cron) \u2192 order flow data (fresh but from bad wallets)\n- `copy-signal-integrator.py` (30 min cron) \u2192 combines into live-signals.json\n- `trading_bot.py` reads live-signals.json \u2192 +1 conviction boost when \"confident\"\n\n**My thinking:** The copy signal was designed to reverse-engineer profitable trader",
